{
  "texts": [
    "Here, the demands for authorship in an essay writing context (and beyond) also depart substantially from the thinner requirements for control that are often pertinent for creating visual outputs.",
    "For instance, in prompting Midjourney to produce 'bird in a tree' Jared neither tries to communicate an idea or claim, nor are there important ways in which 'bird in a tree' has deeper, hidden meanings that Jared might be unaware of and unable to control.",
    "Jared simply wants an image of a bird in a tree that looks nice, and if we think the image has contents at all that go beyond mere form (e.g.",
    "designating a bird that is in a tree), these can be read off from its form in a straightforward fashion (i.e.",
    "pixels arranged in relevant way)."
  ]
}